State governments in the federation has received another round of performance- based grants in the sum of N123.348 billion under States Fiscal Transparency Accountability and Sustainability (SFTAS) Programme for Results. Finance, Budget and National Planning Minister, Mrs. Zainab Ahmed, who disclosed this in a statement signed by Mr. Hassan Dodo, Director of Information, in Abuja on Wednesday, explained that the disbursement followed the achievement of results by the states in the just concluded 2019 Annual Performance Assessment (APA).